thought: Set the parameters for reading Google Sheets to get commercial entries from the specified document and sheet name.
plan: Set documentId mode to 'id' and value to given document ID.
Set sheetName mode to 'id' and value to given sheet name.
Leave filtersUI and options empty for full sheet read.
Test reading to confirm output format.
criticism: Currently no filters or options are set, so all rows will be read. This is acceptable for now but may need refinement if sheet is large.

tool_input.comments: Read commercial entries from Google Sheets with specified document ID and sheet name.
